
Usage:

	auth sufficient pam_portauth.so

Behaviour:

	if pam_env variable OG-PMSHELL (portname) is unset or empty
	   return PAM_IGNORE
	otherwise if the username is empty
	   returns PAM_IGNORE
	otherwise if an entry <username>:<portname> is in /etc/config/portauth
	   return PAM_SUCCESS
	otherwise
	   PAM_DENIED

Format of the /etc/config/portauth file:

	unauth:<portname>

